	(gr_text_box "USB differential impedance calculation done with Sierra Circuits' Proto Express impedance app.\nThe differential pair is routed as coplanar uncoated microstrip differential pair with the following parameters:\n- Signal layer: TOP\n- Reference layer: IN2 (GND)\n- Dielectric height: 0.23 mm / 9.055118 mils\n- Dielectric constant: 4.25\n- Trace width: 0.241 mm / 9.5 mils\n- ΔW (width difference between trace bottom and trace top): 0\n- Trace thickness: 0.035 mm / 1.378 mils\n- Trace separation: 0.125 mm / 4.9213 mils\n- Conductor spacing (between trace and coplanar ground): 0.125 mm / 4.9213 mils\n- Conductor width: 2.54 mm / 100 mils\n- Target diff. impedance (Zd): 90 Ω"
		(start 14.543325 172.0234)
		(end 88.203325 192.8768)
		(margins 0 0 0 0)
		(layer "Cmts.User")
		(uuid "cba2b8f4-0b6f-4305-ab9b-548284b69b2b")
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1 1)
				(thickness 0.15)
			)
			(justify left top)
		)
		(border no)
		(stroke
			(width 0)
			(type solid)
		)
	)
	(gr_text_box "Antenna feedline impedance calculation done with Sierra Circuits' Proto Express impedance app.\nThe feedline is routed as coplanar uncoated microstrip single ended with the following parameters:\n- Signal layer: TOP\n- Reference layer: BOT (GND)\n- Dielectric height: 1.54 mm / 60.6298 mils\n- Dielectric constant: 4.25\n- Trace width: 0.7 mm / 27.7 mils\n- ΔW (width difference between trace bottom and trace top): 0\n- Trace thickness: 0.035 mm / 1.378 mils\n- Coplanar separation: 0.128 mm / 5.0394 mils\n- Coplanar width: 2.54 mm / 100 mils\n- Target SE impedance (Zo): 50 Ω"
		(start 88.203325 172.0234)
		(end 161.863325 192.8768)
		(margins 0 0 0 0)
		(layer "Cmts.User")
